INSERT INTO account_stats(account_id, following_count, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (111361349350846400, 1, now(), now()) ON CONFLICT (account_id) DO UPDATE SET following_count = account_stats.following_count + 1, updated_at = now() RETURNING id;

INSERT INTO account_stats(account_id, followers_count, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (111361349350846399, 1, now(), now()) ON CONFLICT (account_id) DO UPDATE SET followers_count = account_stats.followers_count + 1, updated_at = now() RETURNING id;

WITH first_degree AS ( SELECT target_account_id FROM follows WHERE account_id = 111361349350846400 UNION ALL SELECT 111361349350846400 ) SELECT accounts.*, (count(f.id) + 1) * ( (( greatest(0, coalesce(s.followers_count, 0)) / ( greatest(0, coalesce(s.following_count, 0)) + 1.0 ) ) + log( greatest(0, coalesce(s.followers_count, 0)) + 2 ) + ( case when s.last_status_at is null then 0 else exp( -1.0 * ( ( greatest(0, abs(extract(DAY FROM age(s.last_status_at))) - 30.0)^2) / (2.0 * ((-1.0 * 30^2) / (2.0 * ln(0.3))) ) ) ) end )) / 3.0 ) * ts_rank_cd(( setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.display_name), 'A') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.username), 'B') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', coalesce(accounts.domain, '')), 'C') ), to_tsquery('simple', ''' A l i c e '':*'), 32) AS rank FROM accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN follows AS f ON (accounts.id = f.account_id AND f.target_account_id = 111361349350846400) LEFT JOIN account_stats AS s ON accounts.id = s.account_id WHERE accounts.id IN (SELECT * FROM first_degree) AND to_tsquery('simple', ''' A l i c e '':*') @@ ( setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.display_name), 'A') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.username), 'B') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', coalesce(accounts.domain, '')), 'C') ) AND accounts.suspended_at IS NULL AND accounts.moved_to_account_id IS NULL GROUP BY accounts.id, s.id ORDER BY rank DESC LIMIT 10 OFFSET 0
